inputs.prompt: A colossal storm front rolls in over a vast, open landscape at dusk. Towering thunderclouds spiral and fold into each other, illuminated from within by electric blue and violet lightning veins. Sheets of rain sweep across the scene, blurring the horizon, while powerful wind bends trees and tall grass in rhythmic waves. The sky is heavy and textured, layered with deep indigo, steel gray, and cyan highlights. A single bolt of lightning splits the clouds, casting sharp, cinematic rim light across the terrain. Ultra-realistic atmosphere, volumetric clouds, dynamic lighting, high contrast, epic scale, dramatic perspective, cinematic realism, 8k detail, film still aesthetic.
